text: Nikema Natassha Williams (born July 30, 1978) is an American politician and political executive. Williams is a member of the United States House of Representatives since 2021. She was a member of the Georgia State Senate for the 39th district. She is also the chair of the Democratic Party of Georgia. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Georgia Category:People from Columbus, Georgia Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:African- American politicians
